textfsm_template:
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value STATUS (up|down|administratively down)
Value PROTOCOL (up|down)
Value ADDRESS (\S+)
Value MTU (\d+)

Start
  ^Interface\s+Status\s+Protocol\s+Address\s+MTU\s*$$
  ^${INTERFACE}\s+${STATUS}\s+${PROTOCOL}\s+${ADDRESS}\s+${MTU}\s*$$ -> Record
